2
00:00:48,264 --> 00:00:48,959
Minoru...

3
00:00:50,441 --> 00:00:51,131
Masao...

4
00:00:52,325 --> 00:00:53,068
Susumu...

5
00:00:54,573 --> 00:00:55,184
Yuta...

6
00:00:56,725 --> 00:00:57,452
Yaichi...

7
00:00:58,697 --> 00:00:59,564
Toyoaki...

8
00:01:00,841 --> 00:01:01,490
Isao...

9
00:01:02,684 --> 00:01:03,653
Ryosuke...

10
00:01:04,526 --> 00:01:05,326
Yukio...

11
00:01:06,481 --> 00:01:07,498
Takahiro...

12
00:01:19,445 --> 00:01:22,070
Please, Master, let's go.

13
00:01:22,978 --> 00:01:24,806
You must think of your health.

14
00:01:27,597 --> 00:01:31,566
I wonder for how much longer I'll
be able to make the journey here.

15
00:01:38,935 --> 00:01:40,865
While I am still in charge,

16
00:01:41,843 --> 00:01:45,093
I hope to be able to avenge the lives of these children.

17
00:01:47,912 --> 00:01:49,201
Just this month...

18
00:01:49,983 --> 00:01:53,436
I have received as many as seven reports

19
00:01:53,744 --> 00:01:55,468
of demon catastrophes.

20
00:02:00,280 --> 00:02:07,381
Even as we speak, my children in the Demon Slayer
Corps are on the front lines taking them head-on.

21
00:02:11,590 --> 00:02:14,505
No matter how many lives the demons snuff out...

22
00:02:16,591 --> 00:02:18,521
what they can never extinguish

23
00:02:19,251 --> 00:02:21,721
are the bright embers of a human's spirit.

24
00:02:23,019 --> 00:02:25,331
No matter how often we're beaten down,

25
00:02:26,576 --> 00:02:30,303
in the end, we will rise up to fight again.

26
00:03:19,087 --> 00:03:21,185
Let's hide our swords under our clothing.

27
00:03:22,172 --> 00:03:23,821
Wh... The train's leaving!

28
00:03:25,959 --> 00:03:27,704
Are the police still around?

29
00:03:28,172 --> 00:03:29,667
We have to go, either way.

30
00:03:29,993 --> 00:03:31,784
All right!

31
00:03:32,224 --> 00:03:34,887
I'm takin' you on, Master of the Land!

32
00:03:35,139 --> 00:03:36,284
Wait, you idiot!

33
00:03:36,519 --> 00:03:37,316
Let's follow.

34
00:03:39,029 --> 00:03:40,702
Huh? Hey, wait for me!

35
00:03:43,666 --> 00:03:45,691
Wait up, you guys!

36
00:03:47,073 --> 00:03:49,412
Tanjiro! Inosuke!

37
00:03:49,545 --> 00:03:50,460
We got you!

38
00:04:03,706 --> 00:04:04,792
Ah.

39
00:04:08,378 --> 00:04:10,075
Uh, sorry, gentlemen.

40
00:04:10,268 --> 00:04:11,326
What are you doing?

41
00:04:11,363 --> 00:04:12,463
Get over here.

42
00:04:12,909 --> 00:04:13,943
Let me go!

43
00:04:21,128 --> 00:04:22,969
There, ma'am. All set.

44
00:04:23,081 --> 00:04:24,502
Ah, thank you, dear.

45
00:04:24,761 --> 00:04:26,163
Sorry to trouble you.

46
00:04:26,221 --> 00:04:28,891
Oh, it's no trouble at all, really!

47
00:04:39,762 --> 00:04:43,207
This Rengoku, he's a Hashira, right?

48
00:04:43,849 --> 00:04:45,549
You sure you'll recognize him?

49
00:04:46,389 --> 00:04:49,218
Yeah. Along with his fiery hair,

50
00:04:49,251 --> 00:04:50,819
I remember his scent, too.

51
00:04:51,419 --> 00:04:52,642
Hey!

52
00:04:52,761 --> 00:04:54,311
I'll tell you when I sense him.

53
00:04:56,779 --> 00:04:57,815
Tasty!

54
00:05:30,403 --> 00:05:31,291
Tasty!

55
