655
00:46:56,345 --> 00:46:57,609
Mr. Rengo...

656
00:47:00,763 --> 00:47:01,731
What are you...

657
00:47:04,391 --> 00:47:07,679
<i>Is this girl under the control of a demon?</i>

658
